<article id="home">
  <%= image_tag "logos/logo-shield.png", id: "logo", alt: "Tailored Republic" %>
  <%= image_tag "background-main.jpg" %>
  <div id="home-navigation">
    <a href="#">log in</a>
    <span class="divider">&nbsp;/&nbsp;/</span>
    <a href="#">register</a>
    <span class="divider">&nbsp;/&nbsp;/</span>
    <a href="/shop">SHOP</a>
    <span class="divider">&nbsp;/&nbsp;/</span>
    <a id="continue" href="#process">or continue scrolling</a>
  </div>
  <a class="page-down" href="#process"><%= image_tag "icons/page-down.png" %></a>
</article>

<article id="process">
  <h2>
    <span class="article-title">
      THE PROCESS
      <span class="strikethrough"></span>
    </span>
  </h2>
  <%= render "home/login_register" %>
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="four columns">
      <h4>Choose your suit</h4>
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <%= image_tag "process/choose-suit.png" %>
      </div>
      <p>Getting a tailored suit will change your suit game completely. It as an eye-opening realization when your suit
        fits properly. <a href="#">Choose your suit</a> fabric/pattern and get started.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="four columns">
      <h4>Customize your suit</h4>
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <%= image_tag "process/customize-suit.png" %>
      </div>
      <p>Make your suit yours. Customize your button options, linings, lapels, and personalize it with an embroidered
        monogram. Consult our <a href="#">style guide</a> so we can help you do you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="four columns">
      <h4>Input your measurements</h4>
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <%= image_tag "process/input-measurements.png" %>
      </div>
      <p>If you don’t know this already, it is all about the Tailored fit. Grab a friend and use our
        <a href="#">simple videos</a> to measure yourself in 10 quick minutes. Don’t have a tape measure? Input your
        info <a href="#">here</a> and we will send you a free one.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="twelve columns">
      <h4>Rock your suit</h4>
      <p>We know you look good, you know you look good. Load a picture of you in your new TR suit to our
        <a href="#">gallery</a> or to a social media outlet of your choice, tag us and we will hook you up with some
        gift card action to the tune of 20 dollars.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<article id="top-picks">
  <h2>
    <span class="article-title">
