<article id="about">
  <h2>
    <span class="article-title">
      ABOUT US
      <span class="strikethrough"></span>
    </span>
  </h2>
  <%= render "home/login_register" %>
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div id="blurb" class="four columns">
      <p>
        <span class="divider">/&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span>
        Tailored Republic, custom-tailored suits for everyman, was born of a journey across the globe. From our adventure
        we discovered our passion: bringing the confidence that comes from wearing a perfectly tailored suit to everyman
        through the Tailored experience.
      </p>
      <p>As we journeyed, we met and partnered with master tailors. We found a way to bring their craftsmanship to
        everyman. We created an accurate, online measuring process that promises exquisitely custom-fitted Tailored
        Republic garments guaranteed to fit you. We stand behind every Tailored Republic suit, and that means it will fit
        you the way a tailored suit should fit. And if it doesn’t, we’ll fix it at no cost to you.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div id="get-tailored" class="four columns">
      <ul>
        <li>SHARE OUR PASSION.</li>
        <li>FEEL THE CONFIDENCE.</li>
        <li>GET TAILORED.</li>
        <li>JOIN THE REPUBLIC.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="four columns">
      <%= image_tag "textures/about-print.png" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

